Ammalu raan ammalu humiun isiqtilauqtangit.
“hiuri!”
Humiun qungasirulikkannirumaliqquujilauqpuq, kisiani hiuri
Quviasulauqpuq imminik nuqqangatittilaurmat niaqunga suli aanniqtummariulaurmat.
“ai, hiuri, nalunalaunngilaq taimainniarnirnik — tampultua taimailauqpuq
Isumaaluktuq -"
